snippet: Stacy Lewis had a one-over-par 73 for a one-stroke lead over Amy Yang after the third round of the Honda L.P.G.A. Thailand in Chonburi. Yang birdied the final two holes for a 71.
abstract: Stacy Lewis takes third-round lead at Honda LPGA Thailand golf tournament; other golf news noted.
